{"word":"G1759 - ἐνθάδε - entháde - en-thad'-eh - Here","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐνθάδε</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">entháde</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">en-thad'-eh</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Here</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"இவ்விடத்திலிருந்து - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"here, hither"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From a prolonged form of <a href=\"#/G1722 - ἐν - en - en/1722\">G1722</a>; properly <i>within</i>, that is, (of place) <i>here</i>, <i>hither:</i> - (t-) here, hither.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}